# CPRS

## Active app (Spring Boot 4 + Angular 20)

```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```

Then open **http://localhost:8080/** for the Angular UI (API at `/api/v1`).

- Root `pom.xml` — Boot 4 executable JAR; builds & packages Angular into `/static`
- `apps/review-platform/backend/src` — API + Drools
- `apps/review-platform/frontend` — Angular 20 SPA

## Legacy (not served)

`src/main/webapp` (Ext JS 4) is leftover from the old Roo WAR and is **not** packaged.
See `src/main/webapp/LEGACY.md`.

Docs: `docs/plans/00-overview.md`, `apps/review-platform/README.md`
